What About TigerVNC?TigerVNC 怎么样？

The TigerVNC Project was founded by some of the former TightVNC developers, Red Hat, and The VirtualGL Project in early 2009, with the goal of providing a high-performance VNC solution based on the RealVNC 4 and X.org code bases. Throughout 2010 and 2011, The VirtualGL Project contributed many hours of labor (probably half of them pro bono) to the development of TigerVNC, in hopes of turning TigerVNC into "TurboVNC 2.0." Ultimately, however, it became apparent that, both from a technological and a political point of view, making TigerVNC into a TurboVNC work-alike was going to be like fitting a square peg into a round hole. Unlike TurboVNC, TigerVNC is not focused on 3D and video applications, so its developers were not generally very concerned with making such applications performant by default. Furthermore, there was resistance to including some of TurboVNC's 3D-specific features, such as automatic lossless refresh, in TigerVNC. In general, there was also just an irreconcilable clash of project management styles. Thus, with the release of TigerVNC 1.2.0, The VirtualGL Project stepped down as a contributor and supporter of TigerVNC in order to focus on moving TurboVNC forward. TigerVNC 项目由一些前 TightVNC 开发人员、Red Hat 和 The VirtualGL Project 于 2009 年初创立，目标是提供基于 RealVNC 4 和 X.org 代码库的高性能 VNC 解决方案。在整个 2010 年和 2011 年，VirtualGL 项目为 TigerVNC 的开发贡献了许多小时的劳动（可能有一半是无偿的），希望将 TigerVNC 变成“TurboVNC 2.0”。然而，最终，从技术和政治角度来看，很明显，将 TigerVNC 变成类似 TurboVNC 的工作方式就像将方钉安装到圆孔中一样。与 TurboVNC 不同，TigerVNC 并不专注于 3D 和视频应用程序，因此它的开发人员通常不太关心让这些应用程序在默认情况下具有高性能。此外，在 TigerVNC 中包含一些 TurboVNC 的 3D 特定功能（例如自动无损刷新）存在阻力。总的来说，项目管理风格之间也存在不可调和的冲突。因此，随着 TigerVNC 1.2.0 的发布，VirtualGL 项目不再是 TigerVNC 的贡献者和支持者，而是专注于推动 TurboVNC 向前发展。

The following summarizes the strengths of TigerVNC and TurboVNC, from an end user's point of view. 下面从最终用户的角度总结了 TigerVNC 和 TurboVNC 的优势。

TurboVNC涡轮VNC

  • Very stable -- has been enterprise-tested and productized since 2004 and has thousands of seats in large corporations and academia (read more about our success stories here.) 非常稳定——自 2004 年以来已经过企业测试和产品化，在大公司和学术界拥有数千个席位（在此处阅读更多关于我们成功案例的信息。）
  • Multiple simultaneous VNC sessions under the same user account 同一用户帐户下的多个同时 VNC 会话
  • Dynamic VNC display number assignment (TigerVNC requires VNC display numbers to be statically assigned to user accounts by the system administrator) 动态VNC显示号分配（TigerVNC要求VNC显示号由系统管理员静态分配给用户账户）
  • Users can start/stop VNC sessions (TigerVNC sessions must be started/stopped by the system administrator) 用户可以启动/停止 VNC 会话（TigerVNC 会话必须由系统管理员启动/停止）
  • The ability to set global security/authentication policies for a particular server machine (including disabling clipboard transfer and reverse connections, limiting the remote desktop size, requiring SSH tunneling, and disabling particular authentication methods) 为特定服务器机器设置全局安全/身份验证策略的能力（包括禁用剪贴板传输和反向连接、限制远程桌面大小、需要 SSH 隧道以及禁用特定身份验证方法）
  • One-time password support (useful when building web portals around TurboVNC) 一次性密码支持（在围绕 TurboVNC 构建 Web 门户时很有用）
  • User access control lists (for sharing sessions with specific users) 用户访问控制列表（用于与特定用户共享会话）
  • More attractive and feature-rich VNC viewer GUI 更具吸引力和功能丰富的 VNC 查看器 GUI
    • Uses the system's look & feel rather than FLTK. 使用系统的外观而不是 FLTK。
    • Provides a toolbar for easy access to common features 提供一个工具栏以便于访问常用功能
    • Provides an application menu on macOS 在 macOS 上提供应用程序菜单
  • Support for the full-screen application feature in OS X/macOS 10.7 "Lion" and later 支持 OS X/macOS 10.7“Lion”及更高版本中的全屏应用程序功能
  • Client-side remote desktop scaling 客户端远程桌面缩放
  • More configurable and flexible full-screen and multi-screen support 更可配置和灵活的全屏和多屏支持
    • Supports offset monitors and monitors with differing resolutions 支持偏移监视器和具有不同分辨率的监视器
    • Allows the user to specify whether a non-full-screen viewer window should span one or multiple monitors 允许用户指定非全屏查看器窗口是否应跨越一个或多个监视器
    • Automatic selection of single-monitor or multi-monitor spanning based on the remote desktop resolution 根据远程桌面分辨率自动选择单显示器或多显示器跨越
    • Allows the user to remotely configure any multi-screen Xinerama layout on the server, or to specify a multi-screen layout using the server's -geometry argument. 允许用户在服务器上远程配置任何多屏 Xinerama 布局，或使用服务器的 -geometry 参数指定多屏布局。
    • In both windowed and full-screen modes, automatic desktop resizing chooses a server-side screen layout that honors the client's screen boundaries and taskbar/menu bar location 在窗口模式和全屏模式下，自动调整桌面大小会选择服务器端屏幕布局，以适应客户端的屏幕边界和任务栏/菜单栏位置
  • Full documentation and complete man pages 完整的文档和完整的手册页
  • Lossless Tight encoding method for high-speed networks (approximates the bandwidth usage of Hextile while using about half the CPU time) 高速网络的Lossless Tight编码方法（近似Hextile的带宽使用，同时使用大约一半的CPU时间）
  • More configurable and flexible keyboard grabbing feature (TigerVNC can only grab the keyboard in full-screen mode.) 更可配置和灵活的键盘抓取功能（TigerVNC 只能在全屏模式下抓取键盘。）
  • Default settings are designed to provide peak LAN performance for 3D and video applications. 默认设置旨在为 3D 和视频应用程序提供最佳 LAN 性能。
  • Self-contained X server code base that is fully integrated into the TurboVNC build system 完全集成到 TurboVNC 构建系统中的独立 X 服务器代码库
  • Better support for IPv6 更好地支持 IPv6
  • Java viewer can achieve native levels of performance by calling libjpeg-turbo through JNI. Java 查看器可以通过 JNI 调用 libjpeg-turbo 来实现本机级别的性能。
  • Fully integrated SSH support 完全集成的 SSH 支持
    • -via and -tunnel options on all platforms 所有平台上的 -via 和 -tunnel 选项
    • Built-in SSH key management in the Java viewer Java 查看器中的内置 SSH 密钥管理
    • GUI support for SSH tunneling in the Java viewer Java 查看器中对 SSH 隧道的 GUI 支持
  • Approx. 8-10x better aggregate viewer performance on OS X than TigerVNC 约OS X 上的综合查看器性能比 TigerVNC 高 8-10 倍
  • TLS encryption using OpenSSL, which has better performance than GnuTLS 使用 OpenSSL 的 TLS 加密，性能优于 GnuTLS
  • Remote X Input and Wacom tablet support 远程 X 输入和 Wacom 数位板支持
  • NV-CONTROL extension support NV-CONTROL 扩展支持
  • Built-in UltraVNC Repeater support 内置 UltraVNC 中继器支持
  • Can connect to encrypted Vino sessions 可以连接到加密的 Vino 会话
  • Direct integration with VirtualGL, which allows users to easily run compositing window managers with 3D hardware acceleration 与 VirtualGL 直接集成，允许用户轻松运行具有 3D 硬件加速功能的合成窗口管理器
  • Built-in SIMD-accelerated zlib implementation, which improves the performance of Tight encoding significantly on SSE2-equipped CPUs 内置 SIMD 加速 zlib 实现，可显着提高配备 SSE2 的 CPU 上的紧编码性能
  • The TurboVNC Session Manager, which allows a user to remotely start a TurboVNC session on the TurboVNC host or to seamlessly and securely connect to, remotely kill, or generate a new one-time password for any TurboVNC session running under their account on the host TurboVNC 会话管理器，它允许用户在 TurboVNC 主机上远程启动 TurboVNC 会话，或者无缝安全地连接到、远程终止或为在主机上以其帐户运行的任何 TurboVNC 会话生成新的一次性密码
  • Built-in SSH client with support for OpenSSH config files and password-less public key authentication (using ssh-agent or Pageant) 内置 SSH 客户端，支持 OpenSSH 配置文件和无密码公钥身份验证（使用 ssh-agent 或 Pageant）
  • Seamless integration with noVNC 与 noVNC 无缝集成
    • The TurboVNC Server has built-in support for WebSockets, so a WebSockets proxy is not needed. TurboVNC 服务器内置了对 WebSockets 的支持，因此不需要 WebSockets 代理。
    • The TurboVNC Server optionally starts a simple web server to serve up noVNC and prints a URL that can be used to connect to the TurboVNC session. TurboVNC 服务器可选择启动一个简单的 Web 服务器来提供 noVNC 并打印可用于连接到 TurboVNC 会话的 URL。
  • The TurboVNC Viewer can initiate connections to multiple VNC servers simultaneously, as well as tile multiple connection windows. TurboVNC 查看器可以同时启动到多个 VNC 服务器的连接，以及平铺多个连接窗口。

Note that we do not track the development of TigerVNC very closely, so if you feel that any part of this comparison is erroneous, please contact the TurboVNC maintainer. 请注意，我们不会非常密切地跟踪 TigerVNC 的开发，因此如果您认为此比较的任何部分有误，请联系 TurboVNC 维护者。

TigerVNC老虎VNC

  • X.org module for providing VNC access to the "root" X display (requires building TigerVNC against the same version of X.org that your system uses.) Our alternative to this is to use x11vnc with libvncserver 0.9.9 or later, which uses the TurboVNC encoder. X.org 模块，用于提供对“根”X 显示的 VNC 访问（需要针对系统使用的相同版本的 X.org 构建 TigerVNC。）我们的替代方法是将 x11vnc 与 libvncserver 0.9.9 或更高版本一起使用，它使用 TurboVNC 编码器。
  • Native language support 母语支持
  • Multi-threaded Tight decoding (investigating, but the feature in general is something of a mixed bag.) 多线程紧解码（调查，但一般来说这个功能是一个混合包。）
  • Alpha-channel-enabled remote cursors 启用 Alpha 通道的远程光标

Differing Approaches不同的方法

TigerVNC, owing to its RealVNC heritage, is really designed to be built against a distribution-supplied X server code base and SDK. There are advantages to that approach. For starters, it offloads the burden of fixing X server issues to the O/S distributor, and there is less chance of incompatibilities between Xvnc and the window managers that are bundled with the distribution (since Xvnc is essentially running the same X server code as the "root" X server.) However, there are drawbacks to TigerVNC's approach as well. The biggest is that building TigerVNC from source requires a distribution-specific procedure, which is typically undocumented and difficult for many developers to figure out. We attempted to work around this by providing a "cross-compatible build" of TigerVNC, but that has a whole different set of issues. It requires building all of the X.org infrastructure from source, which is very slow and cumbersome, and if any issues are discovered in that specific X.org code base, they are difficult to address without upgrading one or more of the components (which creates all new issues.) Additionally, the cross-compatible build required a separate static build of GnuTLS and, on some platforms, gettext, which required the maintainer to keep abreast of security changes in those packages. In short, TigerVNC is really meant to be supplied by an O/S distributor. TigerVNC，由于其 RealVNC 的传统，真正被设计为针对分发提供的 X 服务器代码库和 SDK 构建。这种方法有其优点。对于初学者来说，它将修复 X ​​服务器问题的负担转移给了 O/S 分发者，并且 Xvnc 和分发捆绑的窗口管理器之间不兼容的可能性更小（因为 Xvnc 本质上运行与“根”X 服务器。）但是，TigerVNC 的方法也有缺点。最大的问题是，从源代码构建 TigerVNC 需要一个特定于发行版的过程，这通常没有文档记录，许多开发人员也很难弄清楚。我们试图通过提供 TigerVNC 的“交叉兼容构建”来解决这个问题，但这有一系列完全不同的问题。它需要从源代码构建所有的 X.org 基础设施，这非常缓慢和繁琐，如果在特定的 X.org 代码库中发现任何问题，如果不升级一个或多个组件（这创建所有新问题。）此外，交叉兼容构建需要 GnuTLS 的单独静态构建，并且在某些平台上需要 gettext，这需要维护者及时了解这些包中的安全更改。简而言之，TigerVNC 实际上是由 O/S 分销商提供的。

TurboVNC's approach is instead to integrate a well-known X server code base into its source tree, so any issues that are discovered with it can be fixed within our project. This means that interaction issues between new window managers and our version of Xvnc have to be addressed by us, not by the distribution vendor. However, it also means that once an issue is fixed, it is fixed on all platforms. Using an in-tree X server code base makes our server much easier and quicker to build, and it puts us in complete control over the quality of the solution. TurboVNC 的方法是将众所周知的 X 服务器代码库集成到其源代码树中，因此发现的任何问题都可以在我们的项目中得到修复。这意味着新窗口管理器和我们的 Xvnc 版本之间的交互问题必须由我们来解决，而不是由分发供应商来解决。然而，这也意味着一旦问题得到解决，它就会在所有平台上得到解决。使用树内 X 服务器代码库使我们的服务器构建起来更加容易和快速，并且使我们能够完全控制解决方案的质量。

Performance表现

TigerVNC 1.2.x, 1.3.x, and 1.4.3 and later can be configured to provide similar performance to the most common modes of operation in TurboVNC (assuming that multithreading is not being used, and assuming a Windows or Linux client. The TigerVNC Viewer currently suffers from a severe performance loss on OS X, due to unknown reasons.) The following table lists equivalent settings between the two solutions: TigerVNC 1.2.x、1.3.x 和 1.4.3 及更高版本可以配置为提供与 TurboVNC 中最常见的操作模式相似的性能（假设未使用多线程，并假设使用 Windows 或 Linux 客户端。TigerVNC由于未知原因，Viewer 目前在 OS X 上遭受严重的性能损失。）下表列出了两种解决方案之间的等效设置：

TurboVNC SettingsTurboVNC 设置TigerVNC 1.2.x/1.3.x/1.4.3+ SettingsTigerVNC 1.2.x/1.3.x/1.4.3+ 设置
JPEG Image Quality = 92 JPEG 图像质量 = 92
JPEG Chrominance Subsampling = 1X JPEG 色度子采样 = 1X
Compression Level = 1 压缩级别 = 1
Interframe Comparison = off 帧间比较 = 关闭
(Rough equivalent to "Tight + Perceptually Lossless JPEG", but with slightly lower image quality)（大致相当于“紧密+感知无损JPEG”，但图像质量略低）
Compression Level = 1 压缩级别 = 1
JPEG Quality Level = 8JPEG 质量级别 = 8
JPEG Image Quality = 77 JPEG 图像质量 = 77
JPEG Chrominance Subsampling = 2X JPEG 色度子采样 = 2X
Compression Level = 6 压缩级别 = 6
Interframe Comparison = on 帧间比较 = on
(Rough equivalent to "Tight + Medium-Quality JPEG", but with slightly lower image quality and more Zlib compression)（大致相当于“紧+中等质量的 JPEG”，但图像质量略低，Zlib 压缩更多）
Compression Level = 2 压缩级别 = 2
JPEG Quality Level = 5JPEG 质量级别 = 5
JPEG Image Quality = 29 JPEG 图像质量 = 29
JPEG Chrominance Subsampling = 4X JPEG 色度子采样 = 4X
Compression Level = 7 压缩级别 = 7
Interframe Comparison = on 帧间比较 = on
(Rough equivalent to "Tight + Low-Quality JPEG", but with slightly lower image quality)（大致相当于“紧+低质量 JPEG”，但图像质量略低）

However, it should be noted that, due to a performance regression, TigerVNC 1.4.0 - 1.4.2 cannot be configured to perform as well as TurboVNC under any circumstances. More information can be found here. 然而，应该注意的是，由于性能回归，TigerVNC 1.4.0 - 1.4.2 在任何情况下都无法配置为与 TurboVNC 一样执行。更多信息可以在这里找到。
